Changes information about a queue.
.HP
.BR testb (9)\ \-\ \c
Checks for an available buffer.
.HP
.BR timeout (9)\ \-\ \c
Initializes a callout queue element.
.HP
.BR uiomove (9)\ \-\ \c
Moves data between user and system virtual space.
.HP
.BR unbufcall (9)\ \-\ \c
Cancels a pending bufcall request.
.HP
