.HP
.BR vtop (9)\ \-\ \c
Converts any virtual address to a physical address.
.HP
.BR wakeup (9)\ \-\ \c
Wakes up all processes sleeping on a specified address.
.HP
.BR WR (9)\ \-\ \c
Gets a pointer to this module's write queue.
